<https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord.ttl> a ftr:Metric, dqv:Metric, dcat:Resource ;
    dcterms:identifier "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord.ttl"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord.ttl"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    dcat:landingPage "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord.ttl"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    dcterms:title "FAIR Metric - F4 - Metadata - Resource has a FAIRsharing record"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:label "FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "FM_F4_FS_HasFAIRsharingRecord"^^xsd:string ;
    dcterms:description """**What is being measured?**

This metric evaluates whether the database, standard or policy resource has a FAIRsharing record. In FAIRsharing, this corresponds to the existence of a FAIRsharing record describing the resource. Expected input is the FAIRsharing DOI or URL of the record under evaluation. Alternatively, implementations may accept another suitable identifier for the resource, such as its homepage URL, and determine whether a corresponding FAIRsharing record exists, for example by querying the FAIRsharing API.

**Why should we measure it?**

F4 requires that (meta)data are registered or indexed in a searchable resource. Representation within FAIRsharing makes the resource discoverable through a curated, searchable registry used by researchers, data stewards and computational services. This metric evaluates whether the resource has been registered in FAIRsharing and is therefore discoverable through its search interfaces and API."""^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:keyword "FAIR"^^xsd:string ;
    schema:about "Not applicable"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:applicationArea <http://www.fairsharing.org/ontology/subject/SRAO_0000401> ;
    ftr:inDimension <https://w3id.org/fair/principles/terms/F4> ;
    dcat:version "1.0.0"^^xsd:string ;
    
    
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
     
    
    
    
    
    ftr:supportedBy <https://tools.ostrails.eu/champion>; 
    
    dpv:IsApplicableFor <https://vocabularies.coar-repositories.org/resource_types/c_1843/>;
    dcterms:creator <https://fairsharing.org/organisations/2281>; 
    
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://fairsharing.gitbook.io/fairsharing/about-our-records/fair-assistance/fair-assistance-for-repositories-and-knowledgebases> ;
    
  
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://fairsharing.gitbook.io/fairsharing/about-our-records/fair-assistance#fair-assessment-of-life-science-repositories-and-knowledgebases-benchmark> ;
    
    
    
    
    
